ama shugaban ƙasa a ranar ga watan mayun to sai dai rashin lafiya da tsohon shugaban yayi fama da ita ta sanya bai samu sukunin gudanar da harkokin mulki kamar yadda yayi fata ba musanman ƙudirorinsa guda bakwai daya tsara na ciyar da ƙasar gaba kafin nan da ƙarni ta marigayi malam umaru musa yar adua ya rasu a ranar ga watan mayun shekara ta da muke ciki a fadar gwamnati dake abuja watanni biyu bayan komowarsa gida daga saudiya inda yake jinya ya kuma rasu ya bar mahaifiyarsa da yan uwa da matar aure guda hajiya turai tare da ya ya bakwai da ya haifa da ita da suka haɗa da mata biyar da maza biyu haka kuma yana da wasu ya ya biyu maza da matarsa ta biyu hajiya hauwa umar radda dan rimi da sallama sarautu ne na bayi a mafi yawan masarautun kasar hausa a kano su ne manyan bayin sarki sarki ya fi yarda da su fiye da sauran yaya don kuwa ya fi mu amala da su haka kum ya fi ba su amanarsa su rike ba tare da wata matsala ba zan ba da cikakken bayani a kan su zuwa gaba in sha allah dong hoi filin dong hoi filin yana a filin jirgin sama da dong hoi lardin quang binh da vietnam filin jirgin sama da ke bakin teku ya yi runway mitocin za a iya bauta wa fasanjoji a kowace shekara akwai gujegujen daga wannan jirgin saman da hanoi da ho chi minh birnin ya bauta wa ofishin kar ar baƙi phong nha ke bang tan son nhat filin tan son nhat filin yana a filin jirgin sama da ho chi minh city lardin dong nam bo da vietnam filin jirgin sama da ke bakin teku ya yi runway mitocin mitocin za a iya bauta wa fasanjoji a kowace shekara akwai gujegujen daga wannan jirgin saman da hanoi da da nang hai phong hu nha trang vinh dong hoi quy nhon da lat buon me thuot pleiku ca mau phu quoc ya bauta wa ofishin kar ar baƙi dong nam bo esperanto lingvo internacia jubilea simbolo esperanto flag of esperanto border created by l l zamenhof date founded setting and usage international auxiliary language total speakers native to est category purpose constructed language international auxiliary language espera